  <brief_title>Comparison of Efficacy and Safety of Repaglinide Combined With Insulin NPH Versus Biphasic Human Insulin 30 Alone in Inadequately Controlled Subjects With Type 2 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multi-centre, Open, Randomised, Parallel, Controlled Trial in Type 2 Diabetic Subjects Inadequately Controlled With SU +/ Biguanide Therapy, to Compare the Efficacy and Safety of Repaglinide Combined With Bedtime Insulin vs. Insulin Alone</official_title>
  <sponsors>
